The paper deals with the capacity region of a network, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The concept of delay in the network is related to the transmission of information over a network, which is also a topic in networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the capacity region of a generalized network, which can be seen as a type of social network (cs.SI). The cut-set bound is a well-known technique in network optimization (cs.CC), and the paper also mentions the use of linear programming in obtaining the bounds (cs.MM).
